    • Constructor Detail

      • Cube

        public Cube(java.lang.String shapeName,
            double sideLength)
        Constructor for the cube class. It only has one sideLength as every side of a cube is the same length. Because the class extends RectangularPrism it passes the string shapeName and sideLength to the it's parent class.
        Parameters:
        shapeName - String containing the user selected shape name.
        sideLength - Length of the squares side.
